items.title: Jigar Patel picks three buy ideas, believes failure to sustain Nifty above 23,500 could exacerbate market uncertainty
items.description: Jigar Patel advised buying Nifty Futures between 23,500-23,475, with a stop-loss of 23,325, targeting 23,800, ad Nifty Bank Futures between 50,000-50,100, with a stop-loss of 49,700, targeting 50,800.

items.title: Stock Radar: Hero MotoCorp, Glenmark, Adani Total Gas, IGL, Cyient, ACME, Delhivery, Crompton Greaves, Honasa Consumer in focus on Monday
items.description: Stocks like Grasim Industries, Sobha, Nazara Technologies, Lemon Tree Hotels, Balaji Amines, ITI, Easy Trip Planners, Swan Energy, Avanti Feeds, Anupam Rasayan India, and Hindustan Zinc will also be in focus on November 18.
